content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5004.7 - Postponement of drawings

State Regulations

The commission may postpone any drawing and publicize the
same if the commission finds, in the commission's discretion, that such
postponement will serve and protect the public interest. Notes
